description:
The race to Champions Paris is nearing its end. G2 Esports, the current VCT Americas champion and one of the top four teams at Masters Toronto, is the first squad to qualify via championship points for the showdown in Paris. Will we see a new champion too? From July 18 to August 31, experience all the excitement of VCT Americas Stage 2!

In Stage 2, every team has a shot at making it through, which means the stakes are higher than ever. Some teams are coming in with revamped rosters, others are looking to continue their legacy of back-to-back Champions appearances, and a few are out to prove their place in VCT Americas is anything but temporary.
